					<strong>Following are the steps in order to start a new scan </strong>
					<ul>
					<li><p style="text-align:justify;line-height:150%;color:#444444;font-size:14px;"><b>Step 1 :</b> Start the Basex server</p></li>
					<br><li><p style="text-align:justify;line-height:150%;color:#444444;font-size:14px;"><b>Step 2 : </b> Start the Redis  server </p></li>
					<br><li><p style="text-align:justify;line-height:150%;color:#444444;font-size:14px;"><b>Step 3 : </b> Start the web application server  which is to be tested (suppose its running on http://localhost:9254/sample/index.jsp)</p></li>
					<br><li><p style="text-align:justify;line-height:150%;color:#444444;font-size:14px;"><b>Step 4 : </b>Go to the scan tab and click upon start new scan<a href="#" id="step04">Click here</a></p><br><div id="step4" style="display:none"><img src="/static/step1.JPG" style="width:80%;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;"></img></div></li>
					<li><p style="text-align:justify;line-height:150%;color:#444444;font-size:14px;"><b>Step 5 : </b> To begin xml injection scan click upon Xml injection Scan tab <a href="#" id="step05">Click here</a></p><br><div id="step5" style="display:none"><img src="/static/step2.JPG" style="width:80%;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;" ></img></div></li>
					<li><p style="text-align:justify;line-height:150%;color:#444444;font-size:14px;"><b>Step 6 : </b>Now fill in all the required fields which will be needed to scan the web application and once all the fields are filled click upon start scanning button <a href="#" id="step06">Click here</a></p> <br><div id="step6" style="display:none"><img src="/static/step3.JPG" style="width:80%;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;" ></img></div></li>
					<li><p style="text-align:justify;line-height:150%;color:#444444;font-size:14px;"><b>Step 7 : </b>Now the tool will start scanning the web application and once the scan is finished the following screen will be displayed .
					.One can see the report by clicking upon the view report tab. <a href="#" id="step07">Click here</a></p><br><div id="step7" style="display:none"><img src="/static/step4.JPG" style="width:80%;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;" ></img></div></li>
					<li><p style="text-align:justify;line-height:150%;color:#444444;font-size:14px;"><b>Step 8 :</b>Here a user can view the detailed report of the tool.It contains the vulnerabilities and other details.
					.In order to view the details of each vulnerability a user can click upon the number beneath the # vulnerabilities tab.As shown in figure : <a href="#" id="step08">Click here</a></p><br><div id="step8" style="display:none"><img src="/static/step6.JPG" style="width:80%;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;" ></img></div></li>
