					<br>
					<div style="">
					 <h4><strong>Installation and Configuring of Custom Proxy - Steps :</strong></h4>
					<p style="text-align:justify;line-height:150%;color:#444444;font-size:14px;">
					The tool follows a black box approach towards  detection of vulnerabilities in web applications and thus in order to obtain session information to carry out State voilation attack detection we have developed a custom proxy and its code is made avalible to the tester.The tester needs to run the custom proxy written in python before conducting the scan.Thye proxy can be run with a simple terminal command :sudo python proxy.py
					
					</p>
					
                   				
                   
					
					</p>
					</div>
					
					<div>
					
					 <h4><strong>Redis Queue installation :</strong></h4>
					 <ul>
					 <li>
					<a href="http://redis.io/" target="_blank">www.redis.io</a>
					 </li>
					 </ul>
