					<br><li><p style="text-align:justify;line-height:150%;color:#444444;font-size:14px;"><b>Step 4 : </b>Go to the scan tab and click upon start new scan.Select the tab that says Application logic Vulnerabilities based scan.It would further open various sub tabs of application logic vulnerability catagory.Select any of the tabs as per the requirement/Catagory of scan<a href="#" id="step04"></a></p><br><div id="step4" style="display:none"><img src="/static/step1.JPG" style="width:80%;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;"></img></div></li>
